sequenceDiagram
 participant U as User
 participant V as View/ViewModel
 participant R as EntryRepository
 participant L as SwiftData
 participant Q as PendingActionQueue
 participant S as EntrySyncService
 participant F as Firestore
 U->>V: Save entry
 V->>R: save(command)
 R->>L: upsert LocalEntry
 R->>Q: enqueue upsert action
 R-->>V: local success + pending
 S->>Q: next eligible action
 S->>F: write FirestoreEntryDTO
 F-->>S: acknowledgement
 S->>Q: mark complete